title: Another You
lyrics:
I don't want you to talk to me
The way you're acting tells me everything
This feels like a recipe
For disaster but it's missing something
I don't wanna know what you did

I don't want the pictures in my head

I don't wanna hear your words

Controlling my thoughts when I'm in bed

Flicking through me, tryna make me lose my mind, all the time

I think about leaving but it's hard to find it



Another you

Another you



You've already rolled the dice

You've been living in paradise for a while now

And I don't know why it feels like I'm stuck

But I don't wanna find out



I don't wanna know what you did

I don't want the pictures in my head

I don't wanna hear your words

Controlling my thoughts when I'm in bed

Flicking through me, tryna make me lose my mind, all the time

I think about leaving but it's hard to find it



Another you

Another you
